3. cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence): The paper mentions Intelligent Vehicles and their behavior, which could fall under the scope of AI. 
4. cs.DC (Distributed, Parallel, and Cluster Computing): The paper proposes the use of Blockchain technology for data management in the Intelligent Transportation System, which could fall under the scope of distributed computing. 
5. cs.SE (Software Engineering): The paper proposes a mechanism for secure communication among Intelligent Vehicles, which could fall under the scope of software engineering.
